casebody.data:
Wednesday, April 14, 1993

MERIT DOCKET

92-1888. State ex rel. Ohio Civ. Serv. Emp. Assn. v. Trimble.

In Mandamus. Sua sponte, cause dismissed for want of prosecution.

A.W. Sweeney, Wright, P.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Moyer, C.J., Douglas and Resnick, JJ., dissent and would issue a show cause order.
